      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior features a flawless original finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, the bolsters are firm, and the original factory scent persists. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is perfect. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive log of every fluid change and inspection. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is free of debris or corrosion. This vehicle comes with all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title. It drives tight, quiet, and powerful\u2014offering an experience indistinguishable from buying a brand-new car.",
